data.description: Absolutely gorgeous, 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home now available for immediate sale! This spacious home features a gorgeous kitchen with stainless steel appliances, plenty of countertop space, updated cabinets, and much more. Downstairs includes a large living/dining room with vaulted ceilings, oversized family room, bedroom with attached full bath suite. Upstairs includes secluded master suite with separate tub/shower and walk-in closet as well as three additional bedrooms (two with walk-in closets). No neighbors behind, in front, or on one side. Open green space right across the street! Val Vista Lakes amenities include an elementary school, jr. olympic heated pool, lagoon pool with beach entry, tennis courts, pickle ball courts, indoor racquetball, workout center, and banquet facilities
